Passwordless login:
On YOUR OWN, EMORY local machine:
ssh-keygen
ssh-copy-id username@cluster.address

Hit <Enter> twice for passwordless login
Or enter passphrase for RSA key

Aliases:
https://github.com/hbwddl/Bash-Utilities/blob/main/Command%20Line%20Aliases
  Useful aliases to bind:
    Logging in to cluster
    Opening interactive terminal in cluster
    Loading module in cluster
    Changing directory to one that you use a lot (or your advisor's /project/ directory)
    Anything you could imagine....

